        "email": "fzago@cray.com",
        "username": "fzago.cray"
      },
      "date": "2016-04-11 23:07:10.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nI have a test where a request starts on the copytool, but is canceled with lfs hsm_cancel. With that patch the copytool is not made aware of the cancelation.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "15584f6fef3d9cc8cd88bde3070ff72ddeefc8e4",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 419,
        "name": "Frank Zago",
        "email": "fzago@cray.com",
        "username": "fzago.cray"
      },
      "date": "2016-04-11 23:31:02.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> I have a test where a request starts on the copytool, but is\n > canceled with lfs hsm_cancel. With that patch the copytool is not\n > made aware of the cancelation.\n\nBy that, I mean the copytool doesn't receive a cancel request.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
    {
