      "date": "2016-04-12 11:43:45.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\ncancel is done in 2 steps, record the cancel request (which will be send to  copytool), cancel the request record, which update the record to CANCELED status. IMO we should keep the garbage collecting, this will help understanding what happen (keep traces for few minutes).\nAre you sure llog_write works on catalog? Did you make a test with a high number od requests?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
