      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Are you sure llog_write works on catalog?\n\nThere were some issues with using llog_write() on catalogs but these were addressed in http://review.whamcloud.com/15316 and http://review.whamcloud.com/15841.\n\n>  Did you make a test with a high number od requests?\n\nI did, but it would be great if others could do so as well.",
